oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Milton. Car in front of Milton home.
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Decorated car parked in front of the George and Abby Milton house in Chattanooga, TN. Car belonged to Abby Crawford Milton. Thought to be a suffrage or women's rights event.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Automobiles; Houses; Events;
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Judd, Chattanooga, TN
